It can feel orienting to get started on a meal plan, but also overwhelming when you encounter a less-than-ideal food choice. One way to approach this is to see your meal plan as something with flexibility built into it. Some days call for more nourishing meals, while others might involve ;
expanded satisfaction&#x20;

Balance is not an all or nothing pursuit. When you come across something special, consider planning around it- or slowly, mindfully, work towards incorporating variety so that healthy eating is enjoyable to maintain rather than exerting negative pressure.
